<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
    <title>Quantum Edge Pro | AI Adaptive Strategy | S/R Scalping System</title>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="https://s3.tradingview.com/tv.js"></script>
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body { 
            font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif; 
            background: #05070f; 
            color: #eef2ff; 
            padding: 20px;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }
        .container { 
            max-width: 1600px; 
            margin: 0 auto;
            flex: 1;
        }
        .glass-panel { 
            background: rgba(15,23,42,0.7); 
            backdrop-filter: blur(8px); 
            border: 1px solid #1e293b; 
            border-radius: 32px; 
            padding: 24px; 
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }
        .header { 
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0a0f1f, #0f172a); 
            border-radius: 32px; 
            padding: 20px 32px; 
            margin-bottom: 28px; 
            border: 1px solid #2d3a5e; 
            display: flex; 
            justify-content: space-between; 
            align-items: center; 
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        .title h1 { 
            font-size: 1.8rem; 
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fbbf24, #f97316); 
            -webkit-background-clip: text; 
            background-clip: text; 
            color: transparent; 
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        }
        .title p { font-size: 0.85rem; color: #94a3b8; margin-top: 4px; }
        .whatsapp-section { 
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #075E54, #128C7E); 
            border-radius: 28px; 
            padding: 28px; 
            margin-bottom: 28px; 
            box-shadow: 0 20px 35px -10px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
        }
        button { 
            background: #f59e0b; 
            border: none; 
            padding: 12px 28px; 
            border-radius: 48px; 
            font-weight: 700; 
            cursor: pointer; 
            transition: 0.2s; 
            font-family: inherit; 
            color: #0c0f1c;
        }
        button:hover { background: #fbbf24; transform: scale(0.98); }
        button:disabled { opacity: 0.5; cursor: not-allowed; transform: none; }
        .whatsapp-btn { background: #25D366; color: white; box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(37,211,102,0.3); }
        .flex-row { display: flex; gap: 16px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 16px; align-items: center; }
        .signal-card { 
            background: #0f172a; 
            border-radius: 32px; 
            padding: 28px; 
            border-left: 6px solid #f59e0b; 
            margin-bottom: 24px; 
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
        }
        .signal-badge { font-size: 2.2rem; font-weight: 800; padding: 16px 0; letter-spacing: 1px; }
        .signal-badge.BUY { color: #10b981; text-shadow: 0 0 5px #10b98140; }
        .signal-badge.SELL { color: #ef4444; text-shadow: 0 0 5px #ef444440; }
        .signal-badge.SCALP-LONG { color: #22c55e; text-shadow: 0 0 5px #22c55e40; }
        .signal-badge.SCALP-SHORT { color: #ef4444; text-shadow: 0 0 5px #ef444440; }
        .signal-badge.HOLD { color: #fbbf24; }
        .metric-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(5,1fr); gap: 14px; margin: 20px 0; }
        .metric { background: #111a2e; border-radius: 24px; padding: 14px; text-align: center; border: 1px solid #1f2a44; }
        .metric .label { font-size: 0.7rem; color: #94a3b8; margin-bottom: 6px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px; }
        .metric .value { font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 700; }
        .confidence-meter {
            background: #0a0f1f;
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin-top: 15px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .confidence-bar {
            height: 8px;
            background: #1e293b;
            border-radius: 10px;
            overflow: hidden;
            margin-top: 8px;
        }
        .confidence-fill {
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ef4444, #f59e0b, #10b981);
            border-radius: 10px;
            transition: width 0.5s ease;
            width: 0%;
        }
        .strategy-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-left: 10px;
            background: #8b5cf6;
        }
        .scalp-card { 
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e, #16213e); 
            border-radius: 28px; 
            padding: 20px; 
            margin-top: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #f59e0b;
        }
        .volatility-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-left: 10px;
        }
        .volatility-high { background: #ef4444; color: white; }
        .volatility-medium { background: #f59e0b; color: white; }
        .volatility-low { background: #10b981; color: white; }
        .log-area { 
            background: #020617cc; 
            border-radius: 28px; 
            padding: 20px; 
            height: 280px; 
            overflow-y: auto; 
            font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; 
            font-size: 0.75rem;
        }
        .log-area.empty::before {
            content: "📋 Select all parameters above to view activity logs";
            display: block;
            text-align: center;
            color: #64748b;
            padding: 60px 20px;
        }
        .chart-container { width: 100%; height: 420px; border-radius: 24px; overflow: hidden; margin-top: 16px; }
        @keyframes pulse { 0% { opacity: 0.7; } 50% { opacity: 1; } 100% { opacity: 0.7; } }
        .live-badge { background: #10b981; padding: 8px 24px; border-radius: 40px; animation: pulse 2s infinite; font-weight: bold; }
        .method-selector { background: #0a0f1f; border-radius: 28px; padding: 16px; margin-top: 16px; display: flex; gap: 20px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
        .param-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px,1fr)); gap: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .param-label { font-size: 0.7rem; color: #94a3b8; margin-bottom: 6px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px; }
        select, input { width: 100%; padding: 12px 16px; background: #020617; border: 1px solid #334155; border-radius: 48px; color: white; font-size: 0.9rem; outline: none; }
        .warning-text { color: #fbbf24; font-size: 0.7rem; margin-top: 5px; text-align: center; }
        
        .floating-ai-btn {
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 28px;
            right: 28px;
            width: 70px;
            height: 70px;
            background: linear-gradient(145deg, #8b5cf6, #6d28d9);
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            cursor: pointer;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px -5px rgba(139,92,246,0.5);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            z-index: 1000;
            border: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
        }
        .floating-ai-btn:hover { transform: scale(1.08); }
        .floating-ai-btn span { font-size: 2rem; }
        .ai-pulse {
            position: absolute;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: rgba(139,92,246,0.4);
            animation: ping 1.5s infinite;
            z-index: -1;
        }
        @keyframes ping {
            0% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 0.6; }
            70% { transform: scale(1.3); opacity: 0; }
            100% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 0; }
        }
        .ai-chat-overlay {
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 100px;
            right: 28px;
            width: 450px;
            max-width: calc(100vw - 40px);
            height: 650px;
            background: #0a0f1f;
            border-radius: 32px;
            border: 1px solid #4c1d95;
            box-shadow: 0 25px 40px -12px black;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            overflow: hidden;
            z-index: 1001;
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            background: rgba(10,15,31,0.95);
        }
        .ai-chat-overlay.hidden { display: none; }
        .ai-chat-header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e1b4b, #0f172a);
            padding: 18px 20px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #8b5cf6;
        }
        .close-chat {
            background: none;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            padding: 0;
            width: 32px;
            height: 32px;
            color: #cbd5e1;
        }
        .close-chat:hover { background: #2d3a5e; transform: none; }
        .chat-messages-area {
            flex: 1;
            overflow-y: auto;
            padding: 18px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 14px;
        }
        .chat-bubble {
            max-width: 85%;
            padding: 12px 16px;
            border-radius: 24px;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            line-height: 1.4;
        }
        .user-bubble {
            background: #3b82f6;
            color: white;
            align-self: flex-end;
            border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;
        }
        .ai-bubble {
            background: #1e293b;
            color: #e2e8f0;
            align-self: flex-start;
            border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;
            border-left: 3px solid #f59e0b;
        }
        .chat-input-row {
            display: flex;
            gap: 12px;
            padding: 16px;
            background: #0f172a;
            border-top: 1px solid #334155;
        }
        .quick-prompts {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 8px;
            padding: 12px 16px;
            background: #0a0f1f;
            border-top: 1px solid #1e293b;
        }
        .quick-prompt {
            background: #1e293b;
            padding: 5px 12px;
            border-radius: 40px;
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: 0.2s;
        }
        .quick-prompt:hover { background: #f59e0b; color: black; }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 48px;
            padding: 24px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #1e293b;
        }
        .toast-msg {
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 100px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            background: #1e293b;
            color: #fbbf24;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 48px;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            z-index: 2000;
            animation: fadeOut 2s forwards;
            pointer-events: none;
        }
        @keyframes fadeOut { 0% { opacity: 1; } 70% { opacity: 1; } 100% { opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; } }
        @media (max-width: 550px) {
            .ai-chat-overlay { width: 92vw; right: 4vw; bottom: 90px; height: 550px; }
            .floating-ai-btn { width: 56px; height: 56px; bottom: 20px; right: 20px; }
            .metric-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2,1fr); }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <div class="header">
        <div class="title">
            <h1>⚡ QUANTUM EDGE PRO</h1>
            <p>AI Adaptive Strategy | S/R Scalping (1-5min) | Top 5 FX + Gold & BTC</p>
        </div>
        <div class="live-badge">🔴 LIVE READY</div>
    </div>

    <div class="glass-panel" style="margin-bottom: 24px;">
        <h3 style="margin-bottom: 20px;">📊 TRADING PARAMETERS</h3>
        <div class="param-row">
            <div><div class="param-label">🎯 ASSET</div><select id="assetSelect"><option value="">-- Select --</option><option value="XAUUSD">XAUUSD (Gold)</option><option value="BTCUSD">BTCUSD</option><option value="EURUSD">EURUSD (EUR/USD)</option><option value="GBPUSD">GBP/USD</option><option value="USDJPY">USD/JPY</option><option value="AUDUSD">AUD/USD</option><option value="USDCAD">USD/CAD</option></select></div>
            <div><div class="param-label">⏱️ TIMEFRAME</div><select id="timeframeSelect"><option value="">-- Select --</option><option value="1min">1 Minute (S/R Scalping)</option><option value="5min">5 Minutes (S/R Scalping)</option><option value="15min">15 Minutes (AI Adaptive)</option><option value="1h">1 Hour (AI Adaptive)</option><option value="4h">4 Hours (AI Adaptive)</option><option value="1day">Daily (AI Adaptive)</option></select></div>
            <div><div class="param-label">💰 ACCOUNT BALANCE ($)</div><input type="number" id="accountBalance" placeholder="Amount"></div>
            <div><div class="param-label">⚠️ RISK %</div><input type="number" id="riskPercent" placeholder="%" step="0.5"></div>
        </div>
        
        <div id="volatilityDisplay" style="background: #0a0f1f; border-radius: 20px; padding: 12px; margin-top: 10px; text-align: center;">
            <span style="font-size: 0.8rem;">📊 VOLATILITY INDEX: </span>
            <span id="volatilityValue" style="font-weight: bold;">--</span>
            <span id="volatilityBadge" class="volatility-badge"></span>
            <span id="strategyDisplay" class="strategy-badge">--</span>
        </div>
        
        <div id="paramsWarning" class="warning-text"></div>
        <div class="flex-row" style="justify-content: center;">
            <button id="generateSignalBtn" disabled>🧠 GENERATE SIGNAL</button>
            <button id="autoRefreshBtn" disabled>🔄 Auto (30min)</button>
            <button id="scalpModeBtn" disabled>⚡ SCALP MODE</button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="whatsapp-section">
        <h2 style="margin-bottom: 16px;">📱 SEND SIGNAL VIA WHATSAPP</h2>
        <div class="method-selector">
            <label><input type="radio" name="sendMethod" value="picker" checked> 📇 Contact Picker</label>
            <label><input type="radio" name="sendMethod" value="direct"> 🔗 Direct Number</label>
            <label><input type="radio" name="sendMethod" value="api"> 🤖 Auto-Send (API)</label>
        </div>
        <div id="directInputArea" style="display: none; margin-top: 16px;">
            <input type="tel" id="directNumber" placeholder="+1234567890">
            <small>Enter WhatsApp number with country code</small>
        </div>
        <div id="apiKeyArea" style="display: none; margin-top: 16px;">
            <input type="password" id="apiKeyInput" placeholder="CallMeBot API Key">
            <small>Required for auto-send</small>
        </div>
        <button id="sendSignalToWhatsAppBtn" class="send-signal-btn whatsapp-btn" disabled>📨 SEND SIGNAL TO WHATSAPP</button>
    </div>

    <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 20px; margin-bottom: 24px;">
        <div class="glass-panel"><h3>🧠 Groq API Key (AI Chat)</h3><input type="password" id="groqApiKeyInput" placeholder="gsk_..."><button id="saveGroqBtn" style="margin-top: 10px;">Save</button></div>
        <div class="glass-panel"><h3>📊 Twelve Data API (real-time)</h3><input type="password" id="twelveApiKeyInput" placeholder="api_key"><button id="saveTwelveBtn" style="margin-top: 10px;">Save</button></div>
    </div>

    <div class="signal-card">
        <h2>SIGNAL <span id="assetNameDisplay">---</span> <span id="timeframeDisplay"></span></h2>
        <div id="signalMain" class="signal-badge HOLD">— WAITING —</div>
        <div class="metric-grid">
            <div class="metric"><div class="label">💰 Current Price</div><div class="value" id="currentPrice">---</div></div>
            <div class="metric"><div class="label">🎯 Entry</div><div class="value" id="entryPrice">---</div></div>
            <div class="metric"><div class="label">📊 RSI</div><div class="value" id="rsiValue">--</div></div>
            <div class="metric"><div class="label">📉 ATR</div><div class="value" id="atrValue">--</div></div>
            <div class="metric"><div class="label">🎲 Confidence</div><div class="value" id="confidenceScore">--%</div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="confidence-meter">
            <div>📊 ENTRY CONFIDENCE METER</div>
            <div class="confidence-bar">
                <div class="confidence-fill" id="confidenceFill"></div>
            </div>
            <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-top: 5px; font-size: 0.7rem;">
                <span>❌ Low</span>
                <span>⚠️ Medium</span>
                <span>✅ High</span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div id="reasoningText" style="background:#0a0f1f; padding: 18px; border-radius: 24px;">Select parameters and generate</div>
        <div style="background:#1e293b; border-radius: 24px; padding: 20px; margin-top: 20px;">
            <div>📐 Lot Size: <span id="maxLotSize">0.00</span> | 💸 Risk $<span id="riskAmount">0</span> | 🏆 Reward $<span id="rewardAmount">0</span></div>
            <div>🔒 SL: <span id="stopLossValue">---</span> | 🎯 TP: <span id="takeProfitValue">---</span></div>
            <div>🧠 Strategy: <span id="activeStrategy" style="color: #f59e0b;">--</span></div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="scalp-card">
        <h3>⚡ S/R SCALPING SIGNALS (1-5min Timeframes) ⚡</h3>
        <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); gap: 15px; margin-top: 15px;">
            <div style="background: #0a0f1f; border-radius: 20px; padding: 15px;">
                <div style="color: #f59e0b; font-weight: bold;">📈 SUPPORT BOUNCE</div>
                <div id="supportBounceSignal" style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: bold; color: #22c55e;">--</div>
                <div id="supportLevel" style="font-size: 0.8rem;">Support: --</div>
                <div id="supportTarget" style="font-size: 0.8rem;">Target: --</div>
            </div>
            <div style="background: #0a0f1f; border-radius: 20px; padding: 15px;">
                <div style="color: #ef4444; font-weight: bold;">📉 RESISTANCE REJECT</div>
                <div id="resistanceRejectSignal" style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: bold; color: #ef4444;">--</div>
                <div id="resistanceLevel" style="font-size: 0.8rem;">Resistance: --</div>
                <div id="resistanceTarget" style="font-size: 0.8rem;">Target: --</div>
            </div>
            <div style="background: #0a0f1f; border-radius: 20px; padding: 15px;">
                <div style="color: #fbbf24; font-weight: bold;">🔄 RSI DIVERGENCE</div>
                <div id="rsiDivergence" style="font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; color: #f59e0b;">--</div>
                <div id="rsiValueDisplay" style="font-size: 0.8rem;">RSI: --</div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div style="margin-top: 15px; text-align: center; font-size: 0.7rem; color: #94a3b8;">
            🎯 Scalping Strategy: Support/Resistance + RSI only | Targets: 0.5x ATR | Stop: Beyond S/R level
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="glass-panel"><div class="chart-container" id="tv-chart-container"></div></div>
    <div class="glass-panel" style="margin-top: 20px;"><h3>📋 ACTIVITY LOGS</h3><div id="logArea" class="log-area empty"></div></div>
</div>

<div class="footer">
    <div class="footer-content">
        <div class="footer-logo">⚡ Quantum Edge Pro</div>
        <div class="footer-text">Developed by <strong>His Grace Technologies</strong> | <strong>Godwin FX</strong> © 2026</div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="floating-ai-btn" id="floatingAiBtn">
    <div class="ai-pulse"></div>
    <span>🤖</span>
</div>

<div id="aiChatModal" class="ai-chat-overlay hidden">
    <div class="ai-chat-header">
        <h3>🤖 Quantum AI Adaptive Strategist</h3>
        <button class="close-chat" id="closeChatBtn">✕</button>
    </div>
    <div class="chat-messages-area" id="chatMessagesArea">
        <div class="chat-bubble ai-bubble">👋 Hi trader! I'm your AI Adaptive Strategist. I analyze market conditions and choose the best strategy for higher timeframes (15min-1D). For scalping (1-5min), I use pure Support/Resistance + RSI. Ask me about current market conditions, strategy selection, or trading psychology!</div>
    </div>
    <div class="quick-prompts" id="quickPrompts">
        <div class="quick-prompt" data-q="What strategy is AI using for current timeframe and why?">🧠 Current AI Strategy</div>
        <div class="quick-prompt" data-q="What are the key support/resistance levels for scalping?">📊 S/R Levels</div>
        <div class="quick-prompt" data-q="Market condition analysis and directional bias">📈 Market Analysis</div>
        <div class="quick-prompt" data-q="What common trading challenges and solutions?">🧠 Trading Challenges</div>
        <div class="quick-prompt" data-q="RSI divergence signals for current asset">🔄 RSI Divergence</div>
    </div>
    <div class="chat-input-row">
        <input type="text" id="chatQuestionInput" placeholder="Ask about AI strategy, S/R levels, market analysis...">
        <button id="sendChatMsgBtn">Send</button>
    </div>
</div>
<script src="js.app"></script>
    
</body>
</html>
